4 (5) The principal leadership development practicum required under this section shall
5 begin on July 1, 2027, for the 2027-2028 school year with a cohort of principals
6 with less than one (1) year of experience in the position. Subsequent cohorts shall
7 be admitted as provided in subsection (2) of this section.
8 (6) The Kentucky Board of Education may promulgate administrative regulations in
